OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with showers
OL,6,Fduring the morning and become more
OL,7,Fisolated during the afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunny spells developing. The wind
OL,9,Fwill gradually ease but remain
OL,10,Fblustery along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FWith clearing skies overnight
OL,13,Fand winds inland becoming light and
OL,14,Fvariable, the temperature will fall
OL,15,Fwith the chance of isolated ground
OL,16,Ffrost patches developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
