OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDrier and sunnier with light
OL,6,Fwinds and clear skies to start
OL,7,Fbecoming cloudy during the afternoon.
OL,8,FOvernight temperatures drop with the
OL,9,Frisk of frost developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FCloudier on Monday with showers
OL,13,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,14,FDrier on Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,15,Fsunny spells. Temperatures around
OL,16,Faverage but chilly overnight.
